# WSP

> Global engineering and professional services consultancy delivering technical and strategic advisory across infrastructure, environment, and defence sectors in the UK and internationally.

## What they do

WSP is one of the world's leading engineering professional services firms, with a major UK presence headquartered in London. The firm provides technical consultancy, environmental services, and infrastructure advisory to government, defence, and commercial clients, and is one of the largest environmental consultancies in the UK.

